{"tid":1828182,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"猶豫緊睇唔睇《乜代宗師》嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-01-17T14:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T16:49:32.000Z","uid":117862,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e9fe7d2fa131b6703625cefd2ea8f712bfc93b5d","tid":1828182,"uid":117862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"其實無論黃子華真黃定扮黃都好，最重要係我哋認證佢係黃，谷撚爆佢個票房。一來可以嚇撚死啲藍絲，二來等啲心思思想轉軚加入黃色經濟圈嘅人見到原來加入我哋咁正。<br />\n<br />\n所以今次睇《乜代宗師》唔係為咗黃子華，而係為咗壯大黃圈聲勢，俾人信心證明黃圈係搞得成，等人哋希望得到我地嘅認證。<br />\n<br />\n再加上佢首《上善若水》，我諗都唔使點討論，be water my friend!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VXim2wqaN38\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVXim2wqaN38&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=5d62b066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VXim2wqaN38</a>"},{"pid":"abd0cd7b00d513c1eefaf672978545fdc823c3dd","tid":1828182,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:44:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">求下大家<br />\n歐美議員日日講野無人理<br />\n今日好多鬧華為鬧中共tweet響task2呀 <br />\n幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=f4ba90d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"15c7195819816bb94c67f93af1dfc407e30e09d6","tid":1828182,"uid":117862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\